                <note rend="inline" type="source">835.796/223: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Armour</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-12-30T23:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 30, 1941—11 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1166. Your 1565, December 27, 3 p.m. As Air France is on Proclaimed List, you
                    should instruct Intava not to furnish the gasoline and anti-corrosive fluid or
                    any other supplies to Air France.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
